bio.openEndedText:
Hello, my name is Ali. Welcome to my Turo Profile.

I work in the Tech field as an Engineer, have been a super host on Airbnb since 2016 and also have been a Power Host on Turo since 2015. We have a great team of people who handle cleaning, maintenance and making sure your reservation goes smoothly. 

We support our heroes! Military members and veterans, please let us know when you make a reservation. We offer extras for our heroes.

If you are planning on keeping the car long term please let us know and we will make the car unavailable for others. About 50-60% of my cars are not visible to the public so the long term renters can keep them until they're done with them with no interruption.

Check in, Check outs are all remote and contactless. During your reservation I will send you easy and clear step by step instructions on how to do contactless check in, gain access to the car and let yourself in, and drop it off remotely. There will be no confusion with me and I always answer questions as fast as I can (please see my reviews). If you are looking for a host you can count on then look no further.

I’m cool, down to earth, positive vibes, easy to talk with, great energy type of guy.

Hi!

First of all, I love cars! I have had a huge passion for all things automotive ever since I was young.

I recently started this small car rental business and am looking to provide the absolute best service. With convenience in mind, all of my cars are contactless pickup/return with a lockbox.

I really love what I do & I ensure you will have the cleanest car ready for your trip!

I live and work in Seattle. Currently working in engineering, real estate, and Turo. I love everything PNW has to offer, the outdoors, people, food.  

I strive to provide the best experience for Turo guests.
Feel free to say hi, my website is sudipbiswas.com

Kyle and co-host David launched PNW Rides LLC to combine our passion for cars and love of the Pacific Northwest to provide the best cars for visitors, vacationers or anyone who needs a great ride in the PNW. We take pride in keeping every car in our fleet in top notch shape. Vehicles are cleaned in great detail.  All our cars have prepaid Brown Bear car washes and as you use our cars you have the flexibility to keep the cars spotless during your reservation if you choose. 

We can deliver to the SeaTac airport or a location in the Renton, SeaTac, Tukwila, Kent, Auburn area, or other arrangements based on guest request.  Just ask us.  We will either deliver the car directly to you or set up a secure car pick up. We've lived in WA all our lives and are always excited to share our knowledge of the PNW!  We enjoy meeting people as they come to Seattle to see this beautiful state. If you have any questions prior to booking just reach out to us.  Thank you for supporting our small business!
I love the appreciation I get. I try my best to do every little thing.

Loves cars, travel, and music.

My cars are well maintained, always clean, and fun to drive.
